MCViNE adapation of McStas library
----------------------------------

This sub-package helps wrap McStas components so that they can
be used in MCViNE.

* mcstas2: python modules to adapt McStas components. Original mcvine code
* lib: mcstas adaptation c/c++ library. Mostly derived from mcstas c code, and some original code.
* mcstas2bpmodule: bindings of mcstas adaptation c/c++ lib. Original
* bin: scripts and applications. Original
* share: adapted mcstas components. Derived from mcstas components.
* tests: tests. Original

For license information, see LICENSE.

For more information about McStas: http://mcstas.org/

For more information about how MCViNE uses McStas components, see MCViNE documentation.
